description:
Applicability
This schedule applies to: 1) commercial and industrial customers for general power use with a demand of 3,000 to 6,999 kW, and 2) services where other Rate Schedules (other than Rate Schedules NM and SG) do not apply. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
name: Schedule XT Very Large Industrial Service - Demand Metered 3,000 to 6,999 kW, Time-Of-Use
